Notebook[{
Cell["PeripheralCycles", "Title",ExpressionUUID->"7d6e2bb3-e1b6-4407-9a06-fb55779b2042"],

Cell["\<\
PeripheralCycles[graph, cycles] keeps the cycles whose maximum cycle-space \
distance to the rest of the bundle is maximal. Cycle distance is \
rotation-invariant (every cyclic rotation of the second argument is tried, \
the minimum is kept). Method -> \"Frechet\" (default) | \"Hausdorff\" | \
\"MeanFrechet\". Operator form PeripheralCycles[graph, opts][cycles] is \
provided for piping after FindCircle.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"2e8cfc67-4e0d-43fe-be3c-b828562e5b69"],

Cell["Setup", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"887a7ecd-7470-45a7-a956-49f354f20ecd"],

Cell["Load the paclet before running the examples on this page.", "CodeText",ExpressionUUID->"35889817-215c-4c8e-9192-9b5394eeb245"],

Cell["Needs[\"WolframInstitute`SyntheticInfrageometry`\"]", "Code",ExpressionUUID->"f76dd756-43c6-4f17-a8fb-462a8d56fa38"],

Cell["Usage", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"cfbb6d12-a885-4e7b-a55e-ae8b034987d2"],

Cell["\<\
Pick the cycle-space peripherals of a separating-cycle bundle.\
\>", "CodeText",ExpressionUUID->"56808d50-30dc-46b1-90ab-d668dcab07db"],

Cell["\<\
With[{g = GridGraph[{4, 4}]}, PeripheralCycles[g, FindCircle[g, 6, {1, 2}, \
All]]]\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"3c212952-347b-4aa8-8f19-f96d81379917"],

Cell["Render only the peripheral subbundle.", "CodeText",ExpressionUUID->"5a61042d-87a9-4d5d-adc7-65754dfbe5a9"],

Cell["\<\
With[{g = GridGraph[{4, 4}]}, InfraSceneHighlight[g, {PeripheralCycles[g, \
FindCircle[g, 6, {1, 2}, All]] -> Red, InfraPoint[{6}] -> Blue}]]\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"82f83fc2-f4fa-4137-8afd-3ed196558699"],

Cell["Examples", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"91e8c990-902c-4d1b-98d5-b5098da741a5"],

Cell["\<\
On the Petersen graph the bundle is symmetric, so central and peripheral \
coincide.\
\>", "CodeText",ExpressionUUID->"3bb7b4e7-dc2a-4204-a3f9-1eed81201a27"],

Cell["\<\
With[{g = PetersenGraph[]}, InfraSceneHighlight[g, {PeripheralCycles[g, \
FindCircle[g, 1, {1, 2}, All]] -> Red, InfraPoint[{1}] -> Blue}]]\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"2329694a-d17a-4a94-8eb3-3c4fa8ad8946"],

Cell["See also", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"55b609d0-9ad0-47eb-8f32-c89ceb30b462"],

Cell["CentralCycles", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"021a8aef-f418-4434-a123-25d470ffc6b9"],

Cell["EmbeddingClosestCycles", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"f0b19938-f4ad-4c92-8dd0-6851d1b431cb"],

Cell["FindCircle", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"0d3ec6b7-4a68-4f7b-a585-a0e6e2cc336f"],

Cell["InfraSceneHighlight", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"cc49a1dc-d731-41f9-90ce-2cb7f6169ca1"]
},
FrontEndVersion->"14.3 for Mac OS X ARM (64-bit) (July 8, 2025)",
